  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>This once steel-forged helm now glints with a silvery brilliance as if perfectly polished. It was an artifact bestowed upon Casper Mathshaw by the Shepherd of Fate.</p><p>The wearer can make their eyes glow a desired color while you wearing it on their head. Additionally, the wearer is immune to certain effects that impact them based on sight and sound.</p><ul><li><p>Effects that allow them to avert their eyes to avoid it; such as an Umberhulk's <em>Confusing Gaze</em> or Sea Hag's <em>Horrific Appearance</em>.</p></li><li><p>Effects that require them to hear Harpy's <em>Luring Song</em> or Vrock's <em>Stunning Screech</em>.</p></li></ul>",
